Class SegmentedSphereMesh

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.shape.Shape3D
        • javafx.scene.shape.MeshView
          • org.fxyz3d.shapes.primitives.TexturedMesh
            • org.fxyz3d.shapes.primitives.SegmentedSphereMesh
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget, TextureMode

    public class SegmentedSphereMesh
extends TexturedMesh
    SegmentedTorusMesh is based in TorusMesh, but allows cutting the torus in two directions, in order to have a banner parallel to an uncut torus. Based on a regular 2D TriangleMesh, mapped to a 3D mesh with the torus parametric equations Crop allows cutting/cropping the 2D mesh on the borders If crop ==0 then a regular torus is formed (thought with slight differences from TorusMesh)
